{"tid":534062,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"想請教去過下呂溫泉嘅巴打","createTime":"2018-01-19T12:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T15:17:12.000Z","uid":129534,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8acb28b9db82aef285406950e071e78a1a483a34","tid":534062,"uid":129534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T12:08:57.000Z","msg":"下個月會帶屋企人去下呂浸溫泉住一晚<br />\n但因為屋企人唔想留係溫泉旅館食晚餐，所以冇訂一泊二食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想請問下各位巴打 下呂溫泉區夜晚有咩好食？求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a40db2ad3d92cd2ce2260f8c09912647837cf5","tid":534062,"uid":129534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:06:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134095bab8e4f88c140107b9da22b866224263e8","tid":534062,"uid":28237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"自駕去過下呂好似無咩食肆，鐵路旁唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b8d3725a1554b2a1db0146851bd67f62e52445","tid":534062,"uid":28180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"下呂去過一次,我記得入左黑之後周圍都會收晒鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n下個月去又凍又餓搵野食好慘架, 問下間旅館可唔可以後加早晚餐喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c2b15545cface206fa112a97eaf5f37019011e","tid":534062,"uid":129534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T13:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自駕去過下呂好似無咩食肆，鐵路旁唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThanks 巴打<br />\n我上網睇啲台灣人blog,話下呂入夜會好靜，怕到時夜晚屎都冇得食，又唔想兩老失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6c2a7580665cd67385901f402f04ea214c6a2a","tid":534062,"uid":137462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep